<span class="line"><span style="color:#FFB757;">Info:</span><span style="color:#ADDCFF;"> New</span><span style="color:#ADDCFF;"> Sequence</span><span style="color:#ADDCFF;"> of</span><span style="color:#ADDCFF;"> this</span><span style="color:#ADDCFF;"> List.</span></span>
